                            ],
                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Battle Port. Fresh challengers daily - today that is me, and tomorrow it is somebody else. The Company built this dock for spectacle, back when it built things for people. Care to test the water?"
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The harbor lends the teams, so nothing of yours goes down with the ship. My rain is already falling. Step aboard when you are ready."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Stern - the docker on shift",
                    Label: "default"
                }
